<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn more about Nagpur Mail, your trusted news source.">
  <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-black text-[#002b5c] uppercase italic mb-6 border-b-2 border-[#002b5c] inline-block">About Nagpur Mail</h1>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">Welcome to <strong>Nagpur Mail</strong>, a premier digital news platform dedicated to providing the residents of Nagpur and the Vidarbha region with accurate, timely, and impactful news.</p>
    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">Our mission is to bridge the gap between information and the citizens. We cover everything from <strong>City Development, Metro Updates, and Business Trends</strong> to <strong>Local Crime and Community Stories</strong>. Our team of independent contributors works tirelessly to ensure that every story is verified and serves the public interest.</p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#002b5c] mt-8 mb-4">Our Commitment to Transparency</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">In an era of misinformation, Nagpur Mail stands for journalistic integrity. We follow a strict fact-checking process and are committed to presenting news without bias.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

